body.name: CARPETNAL White Dresser, Modern Dresser for Bedroom, 6 Drawer Double Dresser with Wide Drawer and Metal Handles, Wood Dressers & Chests of Drawers for Hallway, Entryway
features: Modern Design: The Smooth white finishes and classic black knob handles provide a unique finish while being compatible with the style and decor of most rooms, adding an attractive look to your living space. Use alone or with other bedside tables, a high cabinet combination is a good choice. 6 drawer dresser brings a retro modern twist to your furniture decor.

6 Drawer Large Storage Space: This white dresser for bedroom has six spacious drawers that provide ample storage space to categorize and store your clothes, cusmetics, children's toys, documents or any other private stuff. The top of the dresser can display your decorations, potted plants, etc to make your room more tidy and attractive. Overall size: 47.3 "(L) x 16" (W)x 31 "(H).

Stable and Sturdy: Made of high quality certified particleboard engineered wood material, each drawer is equipped with a smooth sliding system. Waterproof, scratch resistant, wear resistant, easy to push and pull, durable, easy to clean. 5 wooden tapered legs provide support for the stability and safety of the entire makeup cabinet.

Assembly & Customer Service: This modern white dresser comes with all tools needed and clear step-to-step instructions. We are committed to providing the good products and services, please feel free to contact us, we will do our best to make customers satisfied.

Widely Used: This dresser not only be used as a dresser and clothing storage cabinet in the bedroom, but also as storage cabinet and TV cabinet in the living room, which is making the room more tidy and beautiful. In addition, it is ideal for small Spaces such as apartments and dormitories.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, easy to put together 6 drawers black dresser
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. First this six drawer dresser is very nice, don’t expect the quality of a $500+ drawer chest, but this one is very good quality and affordable. It came in a million pieces but once I understood it, it was ok. Beautiful after it was built. Only thing I wish the knots were silver not gold but is not a big deal.Seems sturdy and the drawers ended up being perfectly straight. I was most worried about that part of the build.A little less than one hour and a half for one person to do, but that’s just cause all drawers comes in many pieces, the frame my husband put it together in like 20 minutes. Two people maybe about an hour or less. But everything comes clearly numbered screws as well as the wood pieces.Another thing drawer guides not preinstalled but not difficult. Very sturdy and is easy to wipe off. Drawers are deep, so you can put everything you need inside them. All in all the finish product looks really beautiful and I love
